name: Excerpts of Deliverance
description:
The 2nd offering from the 'massive metal machine', SEVENTH CALLING.  Excerpts serves up the goods with songs like:
Soul Eater
Fate's Hammer
Deliverance

Members:
Steve Handel-Lead Vocals/Lead Guitar
Jamie Strobach- Drums/Percussion
Michael Poplees- Bass Guitars

Guest appearances:

Alex Ritchey
Ryan McAtee

name: Monuments
description:
The debut release of SEVENTH CALLING.  An inspired call to 'heavy metal' with all the dark production to go with this onslaught of 'in your face' music, delivered in top form.

Released in 2007 on Melissa Records, MONUMENTS will satisfy any true metalhead, starving for excellent tunes.

name: Epidemic
description:
The second 'full length' effort from this killer metal outfit.  EPIDEMIC is a great offering in the style of the great bands like, Metal Church, Judas Priest, Testament, Mercyful Fate, and more........  

Featuring songs:
Epidemic
Paid In Blood
Beyond the Wicked Lies

limited supply only

name: Prelude To Madness
description: The third offering from the USA metal juggernaut, Seventh Calling, Prelude To Madness is a short,  crushing display of classic style heavy metal, featuring, Lost, Deliverance, and Blood of the Divine.  Also included: Blood of the Divine music video, and extra wallpapers for your computer.
